WEBVTT

1
00:00:54.570 --> 00:00:56.570
<font color="#707070">I don't know about you,
it's just too hot today, isn't it?</font>

2
00:00:57.570 --> 00:01:01.570
<font color="#707070">And it's going to get even worse. Temperatures in the mid-30s Celsius....</font>

3
00:01:01.570 --> 00:01:05.570
<font color="#707070">....that's the mid-90s Fahrenheit, tomorrow, maybe even hitting 100.</font>

4
00:01:05.570 --> 00:01:08.570
<font color="#707070">So, please, remember to cover up and stay cool....</font>

5
00:01:08.570 --> 00:01:11.570
<font color="#707070">....with the hottest hits on your FM dial.</font>

6
00:01:11.245 --> 00:01:13.998
<font color="#707070">Come on, guys, time to go home.</font>

7
00:01:14.749 --> 00:01:16.876
<font color="#707070">Come on, love, off you get.</font>

8
00:01:18.836 --> 00:01:22.256
<font color="#707070">~ Do we have to?
~ Yes, we do.</font>

9
00:01:22.882 --> 00:01:25.802
<font color="#707070">I'll make you your favorite dinner to compensate.</font>

10
00:01:27.178 --> 00:01:28.846
<font color="#707070">He squealed like a pig, didn't he?</font>

11
00:01:29.013 --> 00:01:32.558
<font color="#707070">Yeah, brilliant punch, Big D. Did you see his face?</font>

12
00:01:32.725 --> 00:01:34.560
<font color="#707070">Hey, Big D.</font>

13
00:01:35.436 --> 00:01:37.063
<font color="#707070">Beat up another 10-year-old?</font>

14
00:01:37.230 --> 00:01:39.732
<font color="#707070">~ This one deserved it.
~ Yeah.</font>

15
00:01:40.316 --> 00:01:44.570
<font color="#707070">~ Five against one, very brave.
~ Well, you're one to talk.</font>

16
00:01:44.737 --> 00:01:49.992
<font color="#707070">Moaning in your sleep every night? At least I'm not afraid of my pillow.</font>

17
00:01:52.161 --> 00:01:54.997
<font color="#707070">"Don't kill Cedric."</font>

18
00:01:55.414 --> 00:01:57.083
<font color="#707070">Who's Cedric, your boyfriend?</font>

19
00:01:58.417 --> 00:02:02.421
<font color="#707070">~ Shut up.
~ "He's going to kill me, Mum."</font>

20
00:02:02.839 --> 00:02:05.091
<font color="#707070">Where is your mum?</font>

21
00:02:05.925 --> 00:02:08.553
<font color="#707070">Where is your mum, Potter?</font>

22
00:02:09.011 --> 00:02:10.763
<font color="#707070">She dead?</font>

23
00:02:11.931 --> 00:02:13.599
<font color="#707070">Is she dead?</font>

24
00:02:14.100 --> 00:02:15.434
<font color="#707070">Is she a dead Pott....?</font>

25
00:02:29.657 --> 00:02:31.450
<font color="#707070">~ Dudley.
~ Dudley, let's go.</font>

26
00:02:34.370 --> 00:02:36.205
<font color="#707070">~ What's going on?
~ What are you doing?</font>

27
00:02:36.372 --> 00:02:39.333
<font color="#707070">~ I'm not doing anything.
~ We're getting out of here, Dudley.</font>

28
00:02:39.500 --> 00:02:41.043
<font color="#707070">Come on, Dudley, hurry up.</font>

29
00:03:31.386 --> 00:03:33.347
<font color="#707070">Dudley, run.</font>

30
00:04:09.007 --> 00:04:10.384
<font color="#707070">Expecto Patronum.</font>

31
00:04:40.247 --> 00:04:42.040
<font color="#707070">Mrs. Figg.</font>

32
00:04:45.919 --> 00:04:48.005
<font color="#707070">Don't put away your wand, Harry.</font>

33
00:04:48.297 --> 00:04:50.674
<font color="#707070">They might come back.</font>

34
00:04:51.967 --> 00:04:54.928
<font color="#707070">Dementors in Little Whinging, whatever next?</font>

35
00:04:55.095 --> 00:04:59.057
<font color="#707070">~ Whole world's gone topsy-turvy.
~ I don't understand. How do you know....?</font>

36
00:04:59.224 --> 00:05:01.435
<font color="#707070">Dumbledore asked me
to keep an eye on you.</font>

37
00:05:01.602 --> 00:05:04.980
<font color="#707070">Dumbledore asked you?
You know Dumbledore?</font>

38
00:05:05.147 --> 00:05:08.984
<font color="#707070">After You-Know-Who
killed that poor Diggory boy last year....</font>

39
00:05:09.151 --> 00:05:11.820
<font color="#707070">....did you expect him to let you go wandering on your own?</font>

40
00:05:11.987 --> 00:05:14.656
<font color="#707070">Good Lord, boy.
They told me you were intelligent.</font>

41
00:05:14.823 --> 00:05:17.951
<font color="#707070">Now, get inside and stay there.</font>

42
00:05:18.118 --> 00:05:22.790
<font color="#707070">Expect someone will be in touch soon. Whatever happens, don't leave the house.</font>

43
00:05:32.216 --> 00:05:34.593
<font color="#707070">It is hot. That's right, hot everywhere.</font>

44
00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:36.887
<font color="#707070">There's sweat. There's stifling.</font>

45
00:05:37.054 --> 00:05:38.972
<font color="#707070">Diddykins?</font>

46
00:05:39.306 --> 00:05:41.308
<font color="#707070">Is that you?</font>

47
00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:47.648
<font color="#707070">Duddy. Vernon, come quick.</font>

48
00:05:48.440 --> 00:05:50.859
<font color="#707070">We're going to have to
take him to a hospital.</font>

49
00:05:51.026 --> 00:05:53.153
<font color="#707070">Who did this to you, boy?</font>

50
00:05:57.574 --> 00:05:59.326
<font color="#707070">Happy, are we, now?</font>

51
00:06:00.661 --> 00:06:03.330
<font color="#707070">You've finally done it.
You've finally driven him loopy.</font>

52
00:06:03.497 --> 00:06:06.333
<font color="#707070">Vernon, don't say that.</font>

53
00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:10.838
<font color="#707070">Well, just look at him, Petunia. Our boy has gone yumpy.</font>

54
00:06:11.171 --> 00:06:13.173
<font color="#707070">I've reached my limit, do you hear?</font>

55
00:06:13.340 --> 00:06:17.177
<font color="#707070">This is the last I'm gonna take of you and your nonsense.</font>

56
00:06:31.108 --> 00:06:33.193
<font color="#707070">~ Dear Mr. Potter.
~ What?</font>

57
00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:38.615
<font color="#707070">The Ministry has received intelligence that at 6:23 this evening....</font>

58
00:06:38.782 --> 00:06:43.537
<font color="#707070">....you performed the Patronus Charm in the presence of a Muggle.</font>

59
00:06:43.745 --> 00:06:45.789
<font color="#707070">As a clear violation....</font>

60
00:06:45.956 --> 00:06:50.043
<font color="#707070">....of the Decree for the Reasonable Restriction of Underage Sorcery....</font>

61
00:06:50.210 --> 00:06:52.337
<font color="#707070">....you are hereby expelled....</font>

62
00:06:52.754 --> 00:06:56.216
<font color="#707070">....from Hogwarts School
of Witchcraft and Wizardry.</font>

63
00:06:56.925 --> 00:07:01.346
<font color="#707070">Hoping you are well, Mafalda Hopkirk.</font>

64
00:07:05.476 --> 00:07:07.811
<font color="#707070">Justice.</font>

65
00:07:20.073 --> 00:07:22.242
<font color="#707070">He's not very well.</font>

66
00:07:34.797 --> 00:07:36.590
<font color="#707070">Sorry, Hedwig.</font>

67
00:08:43.783 --> 00:08:45.577
<font color="#707070">Very clean, these Muggles.</font>

68
00:08:45.952 --> 00:08:48.830
<font color="#707070">~ Tonks, for God's sake.
~ Unnatural.</font>

69
00:08:52.792 --> 00:08:54.335
<font color="#707070">Professor Moody.</font>

70
00:08:54.794 --> 00:08:57.839
<font color="#707070">~ What are you doing here?
~ Rescuing you, of course.</font>

71
00:09:00.717 --> 00:09:03.428
<font color="#707070">But where are we going?
The letter said I've been expelled.</font>

72
00:09:03.595 --> 00:09:06.014
<font color="#707070">You haven't been. Not yet. Kingsley, you take point.</font>

73
00:09:06.181 --> 00:09:07.223
<font color="#707070">But the letter said....</font>

74
00:09:07.390 --> 00:09:10.393
<font color="#707070">Dumbledore persuaded the minister to suspend your expulsion....</font>

75
00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:12.729
<font color="#707070">....pending a formal hearing.
~ A hearing?</font>

76
00:09:12.896 --> 00:09:16.274
<font color="#707070">Don't worry. We'll explain everything when we get back to headquarters.</font>

77
00:09:16.441 --> 00:09:18.735
<font color="#707070">Not here, Nymphadora.</font>

78
00:09:18.902 --> 00:09:22.739
<font color="#707070">Don't call me Nymphadora.</font>

79
00:09:28.077 --> 00:09:32.207
<font color="#707070">Stay in formation, everyone. Don't break ranks if one of us is killed.</font>

80
00:10:21.965 --> 00:10:24.050
<font color="#707070">Come on, you, around the corner.</font>

81
00:10:26.094 --> 00:10:27.554
<font color="#707070">Come on.</font>

82
00:11:06.968 --> 00:11:08.761
<font color="#707070">In you go, son.</font>

83
00:11:10.305 --> 00:11:11.806
<font color="#707070">There've been no sightings.</font>

84
00:11:11.973 --> 00:11:13.683
<font color="#707070">No deaths. No proof.</font>

85
00:11:13.850 --> 00:11:16.728
<font color="#707070">He almost killed Harry.
If that isn't proof enough....</font>

86
00:11:16.895 --> 00:11:20.815
<font color="#707070">Yes, but guarding you-know-what is the most important....</font>

87
00:11:23.109 --> 00:11:25.528
<font color="#707070">We must trust Dumbledore on this.</font>

88
00:11:25.695 --> 00:11:30.116
<font color="#707070">Was he able to protect Harry last year? Tonight I say it's time to take action.</font>

89
00:11:30.283 --> 00:11:33.495
<font color="#707070">Cornelius Fudge is a politician first and a wizard second.</font>

90
00:11:33.661 --> 00:11:36.831
<font color="#707070">~ His instinct would be to ignore it....
~ Keep your voices down.</font>

91
00:11:36.998 --> 00:11:41.419
<font color="#707070">He's getting stronger and stronger by the minute. We have to act now.</font>

92
00:11:45.381 --> 00:11:47.675
<font color="#707070">~ Harry.
~ Mrs. Weasley.</font>

93
00:11:50.345 --> 00:11:52.847
<font color="#707070">Heavens, you're all right.</font>

94
00:11:56.351 --> 00:12:00.063
<font color="#707070">Bit peaky, but I'm afraid dinner will wait until after the meeting's finished.</font>

95
00:12:00.230 --> 00:12:05.360
<font color="#707070">Nope. No time to explain.
Straight upstairs, first door on the left.</font>

96
00:12:05.735 --> 00:12:07.195
<font color="#707070">Yeah.</font>

97
00:12:09.447 --> 00:12:14.661
<font color="#707070">Mudblood, werewolves,
traitors, thieves.</font>

98
00:12:14.828 --> 00:12:19.707
<font color="#707070">If my poor mistress
knew the scum they let into her house....</font>

99
00:12:19.874 --> 00:12:22.168
<font color="#707070">....what would she say to old Kreacher?</font>

100
00:12:23.211 --> 00:12:26.214
<font color="#707070">Oh, the shame.</font>

101
00:12:38.601 --> 00:12:41.312
<font color="#707070">~ Freaks.
~ There, there, mistress.</font>

102
00:12:41.521 --> 00:12:44.899
<font color="#707070">Scum of the earth.
Not like it was in the days of my fathers.</font>

103
00:12:45.066 --> 00:12:47.694
<font color="#707070">Kreacher is here.</font>

104
00:12:51.739 --> 00:12:53.199
<font color="#707070">Oh, Harry.</font>

105
00:12:55.994 --> 00:12:59.831
<font color="#707070">Are you all right? We overheard them talking about the Dementor attack.</font>

106
00:12:59.998 --> 00:13:02.834
<font color="#707070">~ You must tell us everything.
~ Let the man breathe, Hermione.</font>

107
00:13:03.001 --> 00:13:07.213
<font color="#707070">And this hearing at the Ministry. It's just outrageous.</font>

108
00:13:07.380 --> 00:13:09.549
<font color="#707070">I've looked it up.
They simply can't expel you.</font>

109
00:13:09.716 --> 00:13:12.427
<font color="#707070">~ It's completely unfair.
~ Yeah.</font>

110
00:13:12.927 --> 00:13:15.555
<font color="#707070">There's a lot of that
going round at the moment.</font>

111
00:13:17.432 --> 00:13:19.392
<font color="#707070">So, what is this place?</font>

112
00:13:19.559 --> 00:13:22.270
<font color="#707070">~ It's headquarters.
~ Of the Order of the Phoenix.</font>

113
00:13:23.062 --> 00:13:24.564
<font color="#707070">It's a secret society.</font>

114
00:13:24.731 --> 00:13:27.275
<font color="#707070">Dumbledore formed it back when they fought You-Know-Who.</font>

115
00:13:27.442 --> 00:13:30.028
<font color="#707070">Couldn't have put any of this in a letter, I suppose?</font>

116
00:13:30.695 --> 00:13:32.906
<font color="#707070">I've gone all summer
without a scrap of news.</font>

117
00:13:33.490 --> 00:13:37.119
<font color="#707070">We wanted to write, mate.
Really, we did.</font>

118
00:13:37.286 --> 00:13:38.329
<font color="#707070">~ Only....
~ Only what?</font>

119
00:13:38.496 --> 00:13:41.707
<font color="#707070">Only Dumbledore made us swear not to tell you anything.</font>

120
00:13:43.501 --> 00:13:45.211
<font color="#707070">Dumbledore said that?</font>

121
00:13:47.004 --> 00:13:49.757
<font color="#707070">But why would he keep me in the dark? Maybe I could help.</font>

122
00:13:49.924 --> 00:13:51.884
<font color="#707070">I'm the one
who saw Voldemort return....</font>

123
00:13:52.051 --> 00:13:54.887
<font color="#707070">....the one who fought him, who saw Cedric Diggory get killed.</font>

124
00:13:55.054 --> 00:13:57.264
<font color="#707070">~ Harry.
~ Thought we heard your dulcet tones.</font>

125
00:13:57.431 --> 00:14:01.477
<font color="#707070">~ Don't bottle it up, though. Let it out.
~ If you're all done shouting....</font>

126
00:14:01.644 --> 00:14:04.146
<font color="#707070">Do you wanna hear something a little more interesting?</font>

127
00:14:05.481 --> 00:14:08.818
<font color="#707070">If anyone has a right to know, it's Harry. If it wasn't for Harry....</font>

128
00:14:08.984 --> 00:14:11.028
<font color="#707070">....we wouldn't even know
Voldemort was back.</font>

129
00:14:11.195 --> 00:14:12.780
<font color="#707070">He's not a child, Molly.</font>

130
00:14:12.947 --> 00:14:15.324
<font color="#707070">But he's not an adult either.</font>

131
00:14:15.616 --> 00:14:18.536
<font color="#707070">~ He's not James, Sirius.
~ Well, he's not your son.</font>

132
00:14:18.702 --> 00:14:20.871
<font color="#707070">He's as good as.</font>

133
00:14:21.247 --> 00:14:22.957
<font color="#707070">~ Who else has he got?
~ Hey, Ginny.</font>

134
00:14:23.124 --> 00:14:25.543
<font color="#707070">~ He's got me.
~ How touchingly paternal, Black.</font>

135
00:14:25.709 --> 00:14:28.838
<font color="#707070">Perhaps Potter will grow up to be a felon, just like his godfather.</font>

136
00:14:29.004 --> 00:14:30.756
<font color="#707070">Now, you stay out of this, Snivellus.</font>

137
00:14:30.923 --> 00:14:33.008
<font color="#707070">~ Snape's part of the Order?
~ Git.</font>

138
00:14:33.175 --> 00:14:35.010
<font color="#707070">About your supposed reformation.</font>

139
00:14:35.177 --> 00:14:37.930
<font color="#707070">~ I know better.
~ So why don't you tell him?</font>

140
00:14:38.097 --> 00:14:39.807
<font color="#707070">~ Get off it.
~ Quick.</font>

141
00:14:39.974 --> 00:14:41.600
<font color="#707070">~ Get it up.
~ Crookshanks.</font>

142
00:14:42.017 --> 00:14:44.186
<font color="#707070">~ Stop it.
~ Get off, you bloody cat.</font>

143
00:14:44.353 --> 00:14:46.605
<font color="#707070">~ Crookshanks. Leave it alone.
~ Get it up.</font>

144
00:14:48.566 --> 00:14:52.236
<font color="#707070">~ Hermione, I hate your cat.
~ Bad Crookshanks.</font>

145
00:14:53.487 --> 00:14:56.157
<font color="#707070">Well, we'll be eating
down in the kitchen.</font>

146
00:14:57.074 --> 00:14:59.410
<font color="#707070">Just because you're allowed to use magic now....</font>

147
00:14:59.577 --> 00:15:02.621
<font color="#707070">....does not mean you have to whip your wands out for everything.</font>

148
00:15:02.788 --> 00:15:04.373
<font color="#707070">Hi, Mum.</font>

149
00:15:05.374 --> 00:15:07.084
<font color="#707070">You hungry, Harry?</font>

150
00:15:07.251 --> 00:15:09.879
<font color="#707070">You sure you're all right, Harry? Gave us quite a turn.</font>

151
00:15:10.045 --> 00:15:12.214
<font color="#707070">Harry Potter.</font>

152
00:15:14.425 --> 00:15:16.218
<font color="#707070">Sirius.</font>

153
00:15:21.974 --> 00:15:24.226
<font color="#707070">This is very, very peculiar.</font>

154
00:15:24.393 --> 00:15:28.063
<font color="#707070">It seems your hearing in the Ministry is to be before the entire Wizengamot.</font>

155
00:15:28.230 --> 00:15:31.692
<font color="#707070">I don't understand. What has the Ministry of Magic got against me?</font>

156
00:15:32.610 --> 00:15:36.030
<font color="#707070">Show him. He'll find out soon enough.</font>

157
00:15:46.415 --> 00:15:49.418
<font color="#707070">He's been attacking Dumbledore as well.</font>

158
00:15:51.253 --> 00:15:56.258
<font color="#707070">Fudge is using all his power, including his influence at the Daily Prophet....</font>

159
00:15:56.592 --> 00:15:59.595
<font color="#707070">....to smear anyone who claims the Dark Lord has returned.</font>

160
00:15:59.762 --> 00:16:01.055
<font color="#707070">Why?</font>

161
00:16:01.222 --> 00:16:03.182
<font color="#707070">He thinks Dumbledore's after his job.</font>

162
00:16:03.349 --> 00:16:05.476
<font color="#707070">No one in their right mind could believe that....</font>

163
00:16:05.643 --> 00:16:08.521
<font color="#707070">Exactly the point.
Fudge isn't in his right mind.</font>

164
00:16:08.687 --> 00:16:11.232
<font color="#707070">It's been twisted and warped by fear.</font>

165
00:16:12.900 --> 00:16:15.319
<font color="#707070">Now, fear makes people
do terrible things, Harry.</font>

166
00:16:15.486 --> 00:16:17.947
<font color="#707070">The last time
Voldemort gained power....</font>

167
00:16:18.113 --> 00:16:21.450
<font color="#707070">....he almost destroyed
everything we hold most dear.</font>

168
00:16:21.617 --> 00:16:25.538
<font color="#707070">Now he's returned, and I'm afraid the minister will do almost anything....</font>

169
00:16:25.704 --> 00:16:28.624
<font color="#707070">....to avoid facing that terrifying truth.</font>

170
00:16:29.917 --> 00:16:34.588
<font color="#707070">We think Voldemort
wants to build up his army again.</font>

171
00:16:35.714 --> 00:16:38.384
<font color="#707070">Fourteen years ago,
he had huge numbers at his command.</font>

172
00:16:38.551 --> 00:16:43.139
<font color="#707070">And not just witches and wizards, but all manner of dark creatures.</font>

173
00:16:43.722 --> 00:16:47.768
<font color="#707070">He's been recruiting heavily, and we've been attempting to do the same.</font>

174
00:16:48.686 --> 00:16:52.481
<font color="#707070">But gathering followers
isn't the only thing he's interested in.</font>

175
00:16:55.401 --> 00:16:57.236
<font color="#707070">We believe....</font>

176
00:16:58.195 --> 00:17:00.156
<font color="#707070">....Voldemort may be after something.</font>

177
00:17:00.322 --> 00:17:01.448
<font color="#707070">Sirius.</font>

178
00:17:05.077 --> 00:17:07.955
<font color="#707070">Something he didn't have last time.</font>

179
00:17:09.415 --> 00:17:11.459
<font color="#707070">You mean like a weapon?</font>

180
00:17:11.625 --> 00:17:15.671
<font color="#707070">No. That's enough. He's just a boy.</font>

181
00:17:15.838 --> 00:17:18.674
<font color="#707070">You say more and you might as well induct him into the Order.</font>

182
00:17:18.841 --> 00:17:22.636
<font color="#707070">Good. I want to join. If Voldemort's raising an army, then I want to fight.</font>

183
00:17:35.107 --> 00:17:36.984
<font color="#707070">Harry.</font>

184
00:17:37.151 --> 00:17:39.403
<font color="#707070">You are hereby expelled.</font>

185
00:17:39.570 --> 00:17:42.364
<font color="#707070">Before the entire Wizengamot.</font>

186
